This application tested only at Linux base through the VMware. 

First of all you will need to open a terminal and paste the following command
<git clone https://kokosg@github.com/kokosg/placements.git> to download the application at your computer. 

Use the commands ls and cd to navigate at placements/Placement directory and checkout what each folder include.

Then select the release branch by typing <git checkout release> which is the newest version of application.

After that you could run the application <grails run-app>. 

At first time it will take some minutes for the grails to load and when it finished, 
a link will be appear at the terminal. 

Copy/paste the link at your browser and the Placement application will appear with a general overview about it.